  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide your team through the 17 week regular season and potentially the Play-offs. Play any number of games from each week. <br>Select your team before using the NFL rankings to decide on your offensive tactics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NFL ranking</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Betting odds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play options - rush, Screen, Shotgun, bomb, side-line, end-zone, hail Mary, FG and punt</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time-outs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flags</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scoreboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OT</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Other fixtures/results</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Divisional standings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play-offs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team colours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Player names</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plaver v Player or Player v Computer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game uses the ZX Spectrum interface.</p>",
